Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.52,0:22:51.69,Penguin_JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,冠葉　やっぱりお前じゃ駄目だ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.73,0:22:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You were no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.11,0:22:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have chosen you.
